{"tid":2296454,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[馬丁短篇郊遊]南涌-龜頭嶺一日遊","createTime":"2020-11-22T13:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T07:37:56.000Z","uid":64601,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d73862215036c849cbfd193a37edd99c9faf1df1","tid":2296454,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:15:41.000Z","msg":"上網睇到有個地方叫龜頭嶺，我同我roomate喺廁格都為之一笑。今星期一於去南涌玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1HCozc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1HCozc.png&h=4cba91e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n粉嶺搭56k小巴已足夠，尾二個站叫落車，覺得自己成熟咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一落車有個小食亭，可以去到再食早餐，沿住一條長車路就去到郊遊徑，個view好正，好有feel<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ev4k5FS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fev4k5FS.jpg&h=dbf02d16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影相一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZaY6gOf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZaY6gOf.jpg&h=367e3d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n慢慢就行到旅程入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vfz98u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vfz98u.jpg&h=472b2510&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行半粒鐘就到屏南石澗，啲水好清涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MUmzqHz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMUmzqHz.jpg&h=5c791260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3F8vdV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3F8vdV.jpg&h=a5a78f6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以學我個毒撚frd影相，但記住要小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GGJRsWz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGGJRsWz.jpg&h=7d6fda12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就係咁行，就會行到去上遊啲嘅屏南石澗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fbsbsWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfbsbsWU.jpg&h=02e98c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AYSSco0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAYSSco0.jpg&h=91690e64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就到樓梯地獄，行九個字樓梯上山<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qX3ueCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqX3ueCA.jpg&h=a8732a37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上到去係一望無濟嘅山，感覺近視少返幾百度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rb4xcpv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRb4xcpv.jpg&h=0ef68e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後重點嚟啦，點去龜頭嶺，條路嘅入口好隱蔽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yf4k5Lf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyf4k5Lf.jpg&h=7bb3f10a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一開始行樓梯都行到骨質疏鬆，入咗去一陣愈嚟愈斜，決定收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />望返後面條路同view，幾乎見唔到路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tSa05Ly.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtSa05Ly.jpg&h=8cc38b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行返正路行到咁上下，就見到城景，都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCa05Mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCa05Mx.jpg&h=5790df66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後搭56B走，最好行去獅頭嶺總站坐會少啲人<br />\n<br />\n結論：建議天氣凍啲先再行，冇咩風嘅時候會想死，好在多樹蔭啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8caa8a15ec18b1a01d8014a84a06f1810f966b74","tid":2296454,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"突出半個龜頭"},{"pid":"de8d22eeac619041ea561017660231f73e695ee5","tid":2296454,"uid":64601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8caa8a15ec18b1a01d8014a84a06f1810f966b74","tid":2296454,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"突出半個龜頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"真，有帶水樽去舉重"},{"pid":"5ba1ed730f0c41826f0ebb38480ae19176ef46c7","tid":2296454,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de8d22eeac619041ea561017660231f73e695ee5","tid":2296454,"uid":64601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8caa8a15ec18b1a01d8014a84a06f1810f966b74","tid":2296454,"uid":189911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"突出半個龜頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:16:45.000Z","msg":"真，有帶水樽去舉重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:17:02.000Z","msg":"我冇抽你水啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99129eb5654b2dc831a216898eccc1e1bdc1ea8c","tid":2296454,"uid":350634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T13:17:52.000Z","msg":"健康10/10"},{"pid":"009e2c0545e395594eeb07460e4b841955f86ef6","tid":